title: Sample_RNA_Pt1,Pt2,Pt3,Pt4,Pt5,Pt6,Pt7,Pt8,Pt9,Pt10
source_name_ch1: Sorted CD4+, CD8+, and CD4+CD8+ T cells from patient reseections
characteristics_ch1: cell type: Tumor infiltrating T cells
extract_protocol_ch1: Cryopreserved melanoma patient samples were individually hash-tagged and CD4+, CD8+ CD4+CD8+ T cells were sorted from each sample. Approximately equal numbers of sorted  cells from each sample were pooled together and labeled with the TotalSeq-C human universal as one sample.
data_processing: Filtered gene expression matrices were generated (for sample 001 and 002 separately) using 10X CellRanger (version 3.1.0).
